		    </td>
		    </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="50%" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Faction Hits:</font></b><br>
		    <font face="Verdana" size="2">
		    You take a hit with one clan <BR>
of gnolls and gain faction <BR>
with another dont remember <BR>
the names and it doesnt <BR>
matter because you will <BR>
always be KOS in Paw.
		    &nbsp;
		    </font>
		    </td>
		    <td width="50%" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Loot:</font></b>&nbsp;
		    
		    <select name="ItemTable" onChange="goto_item(this);">
		    <option value="">Select Item</option>
		    
		    <option value="55461">Robe of the Ishva</option>
		    
		    </select>
		    
		    <br>
		    <font face="Verdana" size="2">
		    The Robe of the Ishva- Rare drop looks like enchanter PoH robe Insidious Robe. 50 Mana 5 charisma worn by casters.<BR>
<BR>
Summon Corpse- Common drop.<BR>
<BR>
Emerald- Common drop. <BR>
<BR>
Sometimes he drops both summon corpse and the robe.
		     &nbsp;
		    </font>
		    </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td align="middle" width="100%" valign="top" colspan="2"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Description</font></b>
		    </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="100%" valign="top" colspan="2"><font face="Verdana" size="2">
			Is a 39 necro with 10,000 hitpoints. Hits for around 90 can complete heal and has guards around him. Hes deep inside paw and is a triggered spawn.
		  
		  </font>
		  </td>
