			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Well, i know Prexus is one of the cheeper priced servers, but the most i've seen this robe go for as far as plat is concerned was about 14k MAX. I agree it is one of the nicer robes in the game. As far as trade goes, a yak would be a good trade. This is an EXTREMELEY LONG spawn, but well worth the effort. If you don't have a lot of patience i don't recommend going after it. The stats don't really matter because if you are a high enough level to kill this MOB you probably already have them all maxed anyway. The Spawn is also VERY difficult to get to without killing at least 3 or 4 people. Since everyone is KOS to everything in Paw, there is no way to get there without triggering something. I asm not exactly proud to say that one of my fellow players holds the record for the largest pull (or train rather) in this zone. He pulled all but 5 Gnolls out of the zone to the zone edge, killed everyone in his path without he himself dying. He was a level 46 shaman. Anyway, this is a very nice robe and i have yet to obtain it with the help of my guild mates.<BR>
<BR>
Good Luck!<BR>
Bamek GraniteBlade<BR>
